The Userimage is generated with a specific seed which should be mostly unique for every user. But it might be the same image for different users.
The user image uses a traffic light color system to display security issues. An image with red color should not be trusted also the conversation might be still secure.
There are different reasons for the color to change, as Bluetooth or using old android devices will make your device less secure.
Also old app versions might be considered as insecure. It is just an indicator to collect possibilities which might make the conversation insecure.